Setup a TDD in Google cloud
Steps followed
1) Created an instance in GCE and allocated resources
2) Setup a docker container on this VM with Eclipse and Java
2) Installed VNCviewer to connect to VM from local
3) Setup a firewall rule in to allow connections from VNC (tcp port:5901)
4) Write java programs and corresponding test cases
5) Run the test cases via Eclipse. Later integrate with Jenkins pipeline for CI
